    <div class="faq-block" id="where-is-ripplepop-based">
      <h3 class="faq-question text-4xl text-gray-900 graphik-bold mb-8 mt-16">Where is RipplePop Based?</h3>
      <div class="faq-answer text-xl text-gray-900">
        <p>
	 RipplePop is based in Chicago and our development team is based in the Philippines.&nbsp;We love our Filipino team, they are incredibly hard-working and diligent.
</p>
<p>
	 We look for at least 5+ years of custom WordPress development experience along with great English skills.&nbsp;Part of our vetting process is making sure our developers have very good English comprehension and writing skills to reduce the risk of any miscommunications.
</p>
      <p><a href="#top" class="back-to-top graphik-bold text-gray-500 hover:underline">Back To Top</a></p>
