   You can find our refund policy on our 
  <a href="https://ripplepop.com/refunds">refunds page</a>.
</p>
<p>
   If you have any questions, please email us at 
  <a href="mailto:mailto:hello@ripplepop.com">hello@ripplepop.com</a>.
</p>
<p>
	<strong style="background-color: initial;">Get in touch</strong>
</p>
<p>
	<strong style="background-color: initial;"></strong>At the end of the day, almost everything on the edges comes down to a case-by-case basis. Send an email to <a href="mailto:mailto:hello@ripplepop.com">hello@ripplepop.com</a> and tell us what is going on.
</p>
